title: Diskeeper 15 1104 Professional Edition 32 and 64-bit Trial Reset
description:
How To Install

========--------=========
 -------  How To  Install? --------

1- Install the program - Double click on "Diskeeper15-Professional-Trial.exe".
2- Do not launch the program. If launched then exit.
3- kill "DkService.exe" from services, and run "Diskeeper Crack.bat" as admin and wait until it disappears. The crack will increase your trial period.
4- Run the program and enjoy.
